<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Student Task Management System</title>
    <style>
        /* Inline CSS added */
        body {
    background-color: #fffff0;
}
        nav {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: black;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        nav ul {
            display: none;
            /* Hide the navigation links */
        }

        nav h1 {
            color: whitesmoke;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .login-signup-buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .login-signup-buttons a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #ff6600;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .login-signup-buttons a:hover {
            background-color: #cc5200;
            /* Change background color on hover */
        }
        p{
            font-size: medium;
            font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }
        h2{
            text-align: center;
        }
        
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav>
        <h1>Welcome to the Student Task Management System</h1>
    </nav>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Manage your tasks Efficiently</h2>
        <p>This platform empowers students to take control of their academic responsibilities with ease. Sign up to
            create an account and log in to start organizing your tasks. Track your assignments, set deadlines,
             to ensure you never miss a due date. Edit and update your tasks as needed, and mark
            them as completed when finished.</p>
        <!-- Login and Sign Up buttons -->
        <div class="login-signup-buttons">
            <a href="/auth/login">Login</a>
            <a href="/auth/signup">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>